@NODE 39v4. " Version 0.39v4 (03-26-96) "

 Changed the ASL Requesters a bit to open with about the same Height
 as the Node Screen has, was suggested by EBOLA and a few others "some"
 Weeks ago, just never really bothered to change it - until now...

 Fixed a small Bug with the new TopCPS per Node Feature displaying the
