@NODE 39t7. " Version 0.39t7 (01-16-96) "

 Implemented an Override Function for the Conference Accounting Option using the
 Account Editor, you can now select the Conference Accounting to be turned on for
 each individual User. A Lot more comfortable if you ask me, needs to be a bit more
