 Fixed a Bug with LCFiles not working anymore (was caused by my Changes
 to the NDIRS/PATHS File readings), works again now.

 Probably fixed the Problem with the new TopCPS Routine which was giving
 Problems on several Machines and caused different Crashes from Time 
